Corporate Events
Flexible, scenic, and fully customizable
let’s make your next off-site unforgettable
Elevated Off-Sites, Strategic Retreats, and Celebrations That Actually Inspire. Studio 131 isn’t your average corporate venue — it’s a creative space built for connection, clarity, and momentum.
Book a Walkthrough
View Our Spaces
What We Host
The Space for Your Next Big Idea
Team Retreats
Strategy sessions with a view.
Holiday Parties
Sip, celebrate, and socialize in style.
Workshops & Seminars
Creative energy meets calm surroundings.
Team Retreats
Strategy sessions with a view.
Networking Mixers
Designed for authentic connection.
Explore Our Packages
View Our Corporate Gallery
Designed for Productivity & People
Yes, We Have the WiFi — And So Much More
Private indoor & outdoor spaces
AV-ready with projector, screen, mics & Bluetooth sound
Lounge & courtyard access for casual breakout time
Custom seating arrangements (rounds, classroom, lounge)
Vendor flexibility: bring your own catering, food trucks, or bar
Optional JoBelle decor for branded styling or seasonal setups
Corporate Pricing & Packages
Professional Impact. Flexible Pricing.
We know no two teams — or events — are the same. That’s why our corporate pricing is designed to scale with your needs. Whether you’re planning a high-impact workshop or a relaxed holiday toast, we’ll help you customize a setup that feels elevated, not excessive.
Morning Meetup
$600 weekday
4-hour rental
Tables, chairs, and venue manager
Get Started Today
Midday Mastermind
$950 weekday
$1,100 weekend
6-hour rental
Light styling, lounge or outdoor access
Get Started Today
Full Day Experience
Starting at $1,400
8-hour rental
Full decor, setup/breakdown, lounge + courtyard
Get Started Today
Popular Add-Ons:
Coffee service
$75
Caterer coordination
$150
Branded floral styling
starting at $200
Bartender & mixers
$20/hr + $5/person
Custom signage or backdrop
$150+
Champagne wall or dessert display
$150
Content creation (photo/video)
available upon request
Download Full Pricing Guide
Real Events in Action
Styled, Branded, and Ready to Impress
What Our Partners Are Saying
Trusted by Teams and Thought Leaders Alike
“Our experience with Studio 131 was amazing! They have so many decor options and they work closely with you to bring your ideas to life! Kelly was very attentive and when we found out we were missing a few items the day of our event, she supplied everything we needed! The venue is beautiful with an indoor and outdoor space that can be turned into anything you can imagine. Loved it!”
– Mandy
“Hidden gem of an event hall! We held our daughter’s baptism reception here. The space was decorated gorgeously, the staff was attentive, and we had the greatest time! So grateful to have found this spot! Highly recommend!!”
– Jessica
“I love Studio 131! They presented us with an awesome venue for our latest event. I highly suggest them to any business.”
– William
“This place was amazing and beautiful for our baby shower! Bubba took care of us and made sure we were well accommodated to anything we needed. Would recommend 100% to everyone. The inside and outside were stunning! Thank you again, Bubba!”
– Marc
Reach Out for a Custom Proposal
Ready to Plan a Meeting They’ll Remember?​
At Studio 131, we believe productivity thrives in beautiful spaces. Whether you need a serene setup for strategy or a showstopping layout for clients, our venue gives your next event the backdrop it deserves.
Book Your Tour
Download Our Pricing Guide

About Us
Real People. Real Purpose. Real Celebrations.
Studio 131 was built by a family—with a passion for helping other families celebrate life’s biggest moments. It’s where connection meets creativity, and where the people behind the scenes truly care.
Meet The Team
The Heart Behind Studio 131
A Studio Built from Love, Loss, and a Whole Lot of Decor
Studio 131 began as a dance studio—but it was always about more than just movement. After losing her mother, Karen poured her heart into creating a space filled with meaning. Through flowers, holidays, and heartfelt events, she found healing—and a calling.
Now, Studio 131 is where joy, beauty, and deep intention meet. From weddings and showers to memorials and team retreats, we help people gather with purpose—and leave feeling seen, celebrated, and cared for.
Explore Our Packages
We don’t just host events. We create spaces where people feel held, remembered, and celebrated.”
— Karen
From Dance Floor to Decor Destination
How It Started. How It’s Blooming.
2015
Studio 131 opens as a dance studio
2015
2018
Holiday decor launches
2018
2020
Weddings & events become the heartbeat
2020
2022
JoBelle Designs officially launches
2022
2024
Home Base Partner Program goes live
2024
Our Mission & Values
What Matters Most to Us
Not every event is a wedding — but every event deserves to feel special. From baby showers to final farewells, team retreats to bridal brunches, we bring heart, style, and service to everything we host.
Personalization
Every event should feel like you.
Effortless Elegance
Planning should feel exciting—not exhausting.
Family First
We’re family-run, and it shows in everything we do.
Explore Our Packages
Real, Warm & Wedding-Obsessed
Meet the People Who Make It Happen
